Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:04.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（圣诞将至）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节礼物的准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好像进行得很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！没问题没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么问题了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是出什么问题不问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么没告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个工作人员就是胡子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  要是知道和那家伙住在同一屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定也会左右为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且一开始搞错的人不就是你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是  都是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一起在外住了一晚啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！这个发展我没听说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样怎样  感觉如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成这样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没发生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～果然旅行能让人变得开放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们在哪里过夜？后面又如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那…那个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个无人的寺院里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人的寺院？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裹着毛毯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裹毛毯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…莫非是两人一条？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人…一条…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的呀  外面又冷又暗  我们又没带钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下只好在那里过夜啦  没办法的没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  到底发生什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会对大家保密的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了真的什么都没发生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的什么都没？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！什么嘛！你这什么表情！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  高野吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败了  我败了  她说她没有告白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是你了解她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你们在赌什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺从事态发展依从自身意志的  深情的Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  期待落空也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人出乎意料的保守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然冒出来就为了说这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  主要是和你来说打工的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在美琴家受了几天照顾吧  要好好报恩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…那倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年这个时候美琴家都会请人来帮忙打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天现场见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想来  我还是第一次打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点紧张起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位打工的朋友们  差不多该开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  晶还没来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被晶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被周防
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫来帮忙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中计了！那两个人到底在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还和这家伙见面  让我到底怎么去面对他啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…接着是把堆放在卡车货架上的装饰品搬下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好不好  得认真听说明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中集中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}然后开始装饰工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}采用两人一组的作业方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}如果有不明白的地方请尽管问哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  遇到不懂的情况该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我绝对不要胡子帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那么  今天一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}保证安全  让我们开始好好干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  看到了没  那个金发女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是模特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…为什么要来做这种工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小姑娘  这个我来拿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺重的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次做这个工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是啊  我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  现在休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吃饭了吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡子  坐你旁边可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工还挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始还不知道晶和美琴说的是什么玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来还能做下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话想说的话就直接说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了没什么吗！别缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！竟然骗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗…我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我能回到以前的生活有一部分功劳在于胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还是应该稍微感谢他吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  可他也应该要把真实身份说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  你不是也没说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  总比一天到晚光说不练的家伙要好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不想再和你扯上关系了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这胡子…果然是差劲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  我算是领悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一和你扯上关系必定会和小满闹矛盾…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  天满
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是来打工的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我是来等人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间就应验了我的预感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐那家伙  果真是个瘟神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理来打工可真少见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是第一次打工哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣  比想象中的好办多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  因为爱理你很能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴介绍我来的  不知为什么胡子也一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？播磨？那真是灾难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那胡子真差劲透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然爱理你也是这么认为的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又脚臭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了制服都没见他穿过别的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又陷入最不利的状态了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  见了女孩子不管是谁他都会乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理你最好也小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了那是误会啊  小满～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那倒没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  前阵子他来我家的时候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很清楚你们的情况  仔细核实过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？这么说来…那个时候他好像叫着什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那家伙是个很莫名其妙的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得他不会做那些违反道德的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？莫非大小姐在为我辩解吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很明白  但是大小姐做得好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这回事啊  小满
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前发生的事全部都是误会啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶  好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  是和晶约好的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意挑这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没有搞错吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:34.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（来自：高野学姐  主题：超紧急  今天活动室大扫除  全体集合）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是高野学姐发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在已经在旧校舍的活动室了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼教室里有个巨大的谜团和精美的圣诞礼物在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快赶紧行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是被高野学姐叫来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别  别过来～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云你也成这样了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们穿到一楼的天花板了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟已经是旧校舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  脚也是晃悠悠地悬空着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没掉下去真是万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云也是高野学姐叫来的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞将至  诸位  此乃吾之挑战书也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就发短消息给高野学姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（不能饮酒的…未成年人啊…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野…学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在这里干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝企鹅它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是多么地饥饿都坚强地凝视着太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:42.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（帝企鹅  帝企鹅科）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…穿着企鹅的服装来这里玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我发出的挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何从这里逃脱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  八云  现在你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…现在我处于一个难以解释的情况中…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我现在在旧校舍二楼…遇到了点麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好我就在附近  我来接你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐说要来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑中马上就浮现出她的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…如果看到这个情况的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云  让你久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  企鹅耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一瞬间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁可以依赖的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  八云  把那个人叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要八云你在  他一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用意念吧  他一定会感觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意念？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事者事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  八云
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  他说过要去配眼镜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  所以才来不了啊  花井学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？花井学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那  怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫爱理她们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理去参加某个派对去了  美琴和麻生约会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那真是想叫也叫不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这样下去如果谁也不来救我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  睡着了要死人的啊  八云婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉婆婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后然后  最终…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？为什么会变大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是企鹅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:14:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  好像没有人对我是企鹅这件事产生疑问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…与其说是疑问…其实在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道我为什么要穿着这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说  学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始你就是可以逃脱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这会成为不错的小道消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们那滑稽又害羞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地收集到这台照相机里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场游戏  看来是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比刚才离我更近一些了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么下去  就真的没有人来救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就要这样度过新年了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在正下方的教室里有人在那里做什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一楼吗？在寒假里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:15:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;6;0;0,比如说 必须马上赶出120页的原稿 但却无法回到自己的家 于是到同班同学的家里寄宿 却一下子又被赶走 还被迫帮别人去相亲 结果工作没有任何进展 最终走投无路 潜入旧校舍创作原稿 也许有这样的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有的啦  那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣…圣诞老人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是体操用的垫子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢？那个圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不足挂齿的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  而且也得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节也才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的衣服借了没还真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  又要找新的工作点了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确感觉到了八云的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  今天是平安夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在这里华丽地放一把烟花吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  已经没时间了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能轻言放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  波摩你真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  今晚的派对有什么节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要不你问问东乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  反正是万众期待的绝妙之物就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  不要总是这样子卖关子嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不过等到晚上再揭晓也很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行啊  我们又不像波摩同学他们那么帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  我们不都是男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们能做到的  我们怎么可能做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉停下步伐之时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待他的就是死亡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想那样的话  就不断奔跑下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义无反顾地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义无反顾地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能注意到自己的弱点  我很赞赏你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来当你的顾问吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  就让我东乡来确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的男子气概到底是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我家要举行舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为自己是男子汉的人可以尽管来参加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是规则
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你  气概还只有一半而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想来  就尝试打动我的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝了？那真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了  他以为自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问可以做一下访问调查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要  而且即使没有女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你看看手相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节里也不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了您的未来  请务必进行一分钟的祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  难道我看起来就那么可怜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…正是这种时候才更要灌溉你干涸的心灵罅隙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有干涸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今就放手干吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田山同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里重生为男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那个东乡还以颜色！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为什么都要模仿波摩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…毕竟这样很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说西本  你再厚脸皮也要适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你还是得出了这个结论啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你们犯了一个很大的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭外表  是无法到达我们的高度的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我们只是小孩子的模仿吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还欠什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波摩同学有时会骑摩托车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吧啦哩啦  吧啦哩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要模仿波摩同学的口头禅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的口头禅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说英语怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}DAS{\r}\N是咧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不识相的薯条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想妨碍你的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…玩笑玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要汉堡包套餐…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉堡包套餐久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不识相的薯条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们来吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉堡包也不识相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁也一样咧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把午饭还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奈良  西本…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  我们…还是做回自己比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不走别人走过的路  而去开创属于自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是真正的男子汉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经成为绅士了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快到我的派对来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…这不是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我们已经重生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  我马上过来  待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…波摩要回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  东乡会让你们尽兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我的小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  连波摩的份一起  让我们好好地享受吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…正如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像大家都有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说起来  这个真是超好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！你们在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来跳舞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我们还练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没能和女孩子打成一片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今年的圣诞节能和吉田山同学你们一起过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…圣诞节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到圣诞节果然还是咖喱对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  乌丸同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  School Rumble 2学期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是圣诞节！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前FOR圣诞节！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧圣诞节！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞咖喱  真棒！
